# Glass Bead Game — environment.
# Copy to `.env` and fill in to enable cloud login + sync. Leave BOTH blank
# (or delete .env) to run fully local / guest mode — no account required.
#
# Get these from your Supabase project: Settings → API.
#   - Project URL  → VITE_SUPABASE_URL
#   - anon/public key → VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY  (public by design; security is via RLS, never put the service_role key here)
#
# Only VITE_-prefixed vars are exposed to the browser bundle.

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
